-- MOVES-Charles McVeigh joins Rubicon Fund Management as chairman
-- By Lehar Maan in Bengaluru
-- Mon Dec 15, 2014 09:40AM EST
-- None



Dec 15 (Reuters) - Hedge fund Rubicon Fund Management LLP said it appointed Charles McVeigh, a former Salomon Brothers executive, as chairman.

McVeigh oversaw the development of Salomon Brothers through its integration with Schroders and then Citigroup Inc <C.N>. He remains a senior advisor at Citigroup's private bank unit.